'''飓风亚历克斯'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Alex}}）是[[2004年大西洋飓风季|2004年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是首场获命名的风暴、首场飓风和大型飓风。气旋成型日期相对较晚，是1954年后所有大西洋飓风季中形成日期第五晚的首场风暴。系统源自7月31日[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]以东海域上层低气压区同下层弱[[低压槽|低压槽]]的相互影响，成型后朝东北方向移动，增强至[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]160公里强度后从距[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]海岸不足16公里近海掠过。亚历克斯接下来进一步强化，在[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]近海达到风力时速195公里的最高强度，成为有纪录以来[[北纬38度线|北纬38度线]]以北出现的两场大型飓风之一。风暴以飓风强度直接袭击[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]的外滩群岛，这里还曾在不到一年前受到[[飓风伊莎贝尔|飓风伊莎贝尔]]的沉重打击。

飓风在[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]产生狂风并引发洪灾，造成轻度破坏。岛上有上百套房屋受损，许多汽车因洪水抛锚。亚历克斯还在[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]沿线产生大浪和[[离岸流|离岸流]]，导致一人遇难，多人受伤，整场风暴造成的损失总额约为750万美元（2004年美元）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Alex 2004 track.png}}
7月26日，弱下层[[低压槽|低压槽]]和东侧的上层[[低气压|低气压区]]相互影响，在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]以东洋面发展出对流<ref>{{Cite report | author = Franklin | title = July 27 Tropical Weather Outlook | year = 2004 | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810093313/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2004/TWOAT.200407272057 | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2004/TWOAT.200407272057 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-08-10 | date =  }}</ref>。两天后，有[[东风波|东风波]]进入这片海域，令对流逐渐组织，范围也相应增大。虽然外界环境还不利于形成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，但系统还是快速朝西北方向移动并稳步组织，于30日发展出下层低气压区。7月31日，系统经过进一步组织在佛罗里达州[[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]以东约320公里洋面发展成[[2004年大西洋飓风季|本季]]第一号热带低气压。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = James L. Franklin | title = Hurricane Alex Tropical Cyclone Report | year = 2004 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL012004_Alex.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002055448/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL012004_Alex.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>

热带低气压的动向很不稳定，环流规模非常庞大，中心附近缺乏深层对流，气旋强度保持在相对较弱的水平<ref name="disc3">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Number Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313045749/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.003.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。中心位移至低气压南侧<ref name="disc4">{{cite report | author = James L. Franklin | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Number Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312235922/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.004.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>，距中央位置更近。逐渐逼近的上层低压槽令气旋上空的[[风切变|风切变]]减少，热带低气压因此在8月1日强化成热带风暴并获名“亚历克斯”（{{lang|en|Alex}}）。低压槽还令风暴加速向东北方向前进。由于风切变少，行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]因[[墨西哥湾暖流|墨西哥湾暖流]]影响而偏高，亚历克斯中心上空的深层对流持续积累，于8月3日在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[恐怖角_(北卡罗莱纳州)|恐怖角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Fear}}）东南方向约120公里海域强化成飓风。气旋继续增强，仅升级数小时后就达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|二级飓风]]标准。风暴逼近北卡罗莱纳州[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]，于3日晚从距[[哈特拉斯角_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）不足16公里位置经过。西侧风眼墙从外滩群岛上空掠过，但中心依然位于海上。<ref name="tcr" />

受[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]气流影响，亚历克斯经过外滩群岛后转向东北偏东，飓风一度减弱至一级强度<ref name="tcr" />，但很快又在墨西哥湾暖流的影响下增强<ref name="disc18">{{cite report | author1 = Richard Knabb | author2 = Lixion Avila | year = 2004 | title = Hurricane Alex Discussion Number Eighteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313084152/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.018.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.018.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | date =  }}</ref>。由于行经海域水温一直比正常水平要高2[[摄氏度|°C]]左右，因此风暴在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]][[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]以南约710公里洋面达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]195公里的最高强度，成为大型飓风<ref name="disc19">{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | year = 2004 | title = Hurricane Alex Discussion Number Nineteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.019.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210548/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.019.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。风切变一直很少，外界环境总体有利，亚历克斯得以保持三级飓风强度，直至5日晚开始经过[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]以南约465公里的寒冷洋面。接下来风暴迅速减弱，于8月6日降级成热带风暴。当晚，亚历克斯在纽芬兰岛[[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）以东约1530公里海域转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，并在不久后失去踪影。<ref name="tcr" />

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Alex_Radar.png|right]]
气象机构起初认为亚历克斯的强度会很有限，针对气旋发布的首份公告中还预测风暴会以热带风暴下限强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Number 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221113/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2004/dis/al012004.discus.001.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。亚历克斯接下来呈现出显著增强趋势，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]向[[了望峡|了望峡]]（{{lang|en|Cape Lookout}}）到[[俄勒冈水湾|俄勒冈水湾]]（{{lang|en|Oregon Inlet}}）发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]，这些地区的风速在收到警告约20小时后达到飓风强度。此外，气旋沿北卡罗莱纳州海岸平行移动期间，该州大部分沿海地区收到热带风暴警告。<ref name="tcr" />

[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]约有3500名游客不顾热带风暴警告继续逗留，但其中大部分打算在亚历克斯增强或逼近后离开，当地没有发布疏散令<ref name="beach">{{cite news | author1 = Ken Derksen | author2 = Web Staff | year = 2004 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114070250/http://rdu.news14.com/content/weather/weather_stories/?ArID=52465&SecID=299 | title = Beach-goers react to Alex | publisher = News 14 Carolina | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | url = http://rdu.news14.com/content/weather/weather_stories/?ArID=52465&SecID=299 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="okra">{{cite news | author = RAI Staff | year = 2004 | title = Alex hits Ocracoke | accessdate = 2012-02-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120206130224/http://www.outer-banks.com/ecnews/2042index.asp | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.outer-banks.com/ecnews/2042index.asp | archivedate = 2012-02-06 }}</ref>。官员建议居民对逐渐逼近的飓风采取预防措施<ref name="aim">{{cite news | author = Insurance Journal | year = 2004 | title = North Carolina Coast Takes on Hurricane Alex | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.insurancejournal.com/news/southeast/2004/08/03/44657.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205549/http://www.insurancejournal.com/news/southeast/2004/08/03/44657.htm }}</ref>。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻[[加特利县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|加特利县]][[莫尔黑德市_(北卡罗莱纳州)|莫尔黑德市]]（{{lang|en|Morehead City}}）办事处在飓风经过外滩群岛前一天发布山洪爆发观察预警，还在亚历克斯行进至距该州最近位置当天向[[克雷文县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|克雷文县]]和加特利县发布山洪爆发警告<ref name="mornws">{{cite web | author = Newport/Morehead City, NC National Weather Service | year = 2004 | title = Hurricane Alex Impacts Eastern North Carolina | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150911045026/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/mhx/HurricaneAlex.html | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/mhx/HurricaneAlex.html | archivedate = 2015-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。面对风暴威胁，[[了解峡国家海岸|了解峡国家海岸]]提前关闭并疏散人员<ref name="clns">{{cite web | author = Environmental News Service | year = 2004 | title = Southeast Battens Down the Hatches for Hurricane Alex | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.ens-newswire.com/ens/aug2004/2004-08-03-09.asp | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184705/http://www.ens-newswire.com/ens/aug2004/2004-08-03-09.asp }}</ref>。[[美国国家公园管理局|美国国家公园管理局]]还将开普角营地关闭<ref name="cpc">{{cite news | author = News 14 Carolina Staff | year = 2004 | title = Campground closed along Outer Banks | accessdate = 2012-03-27 | archivedate = 2012-03-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120327142027/http://triangle.news14.com/content/52466/campground-closed-along-outer-banks | url = http://triangle.news14.com/content/52466/campground-closed-along-outer-banks }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Alex_03_aug_2004_1600Z.jpg|left]]
亚历克斯在佛罗里达州近海飘移期间就给北卡罗莱纳州海岸沿线带去大浪和[[离岸流|离岸流]]，导致九人需救生员救援<ref name="beach" />。行经[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]期间，[[巴克斯顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|巴克斯顿]]（{{lang|en|Buxton}}）和[[奥克拉科克_(北卡罗莱纳州)|奥克拉科克村]]（{{lang|en|Ocracoke Village}}）靠[[帕姆利科湾|帕姆利科湾]]（{{lang|en|Pamlico Sound}}）一侧出现1.8米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]。奥克拉科克岛上发生19年前[[飓风格洛丽亚|飓风格洛丽亚]]过后最严重的洪灾。外滩群岛其他地区水位普遍比正常水平高出0.6至1.2米。沿海地区降雨量超过127毫米，其中奥克拉科克达到192毫米。莫尔黑德市测得的最大持续风速达到每小时124公里，阵风时速则有169公里。<ref name="tcr" />北卡罗莱纳州大部分沿海地区出现轻度[[海蚀|海滩侵蚀]]，并且奥克拉科克岛的程度特别严重<ref name="mornws" />。

恐怖角出现轻度海滩侵蚀，[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀作用]]同大浪共同影响，将一条道路的部分路段冲毁<ref name="capefear">{{cite web | author = Wilmington National Weather Service | year = 2004 | title = Hurricane Alex Port Tropical Cyclone Report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150512155346/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/08-03-04/PSHILM.txt | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/08-03-04/PSHILM.txt | archivedate = 2015-05-12 }}</ref>。外滩群岛有200余辆汽车因暴雨抛锚<ref name="okra" />，另有近500辆被淹<ref name="sd3">{{cite journal | year = 2004-08 | title = Storm data and unusual weather phenomena | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | volume = 46 | number = 8 | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-361696A8-0F69-416E-A32E-F7B108A6B305.pdf | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | editor1 = William Angel | editor2 = Stuart Hinson | editor3 = Rhonda Herndon | issn = 0039-1972 | author = National Climatic Data Center | journal = Storm Data | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810150936/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-361696A8-0F69-416E-A32E-F7B108A6B305.pdf | archivedate = 2016-08-10 }}</ref>。强烈的阵风致使约一万套建筑断电<ref name="power">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | year = 2004 | title = Hurricane Alex leaving thousands in the dark | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114065818/http://rdu.news14.com/content/weather/weather_stories/?ArID=52524&SecID=299 | url = http://rdu.news14.com/content/weather/weather_stories/?ArID=52524&SecID=299 }}</ref>，许多地方在风暴过去两到三天后仍未恢复<ref name="mornws" />。狂风和风暴潮共同影响，令上百套房屋及其他建筑受损，损失总额约为750万美元（2004年美元）<ref name="sd3" />。气旋过去两天后，[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]][[纳格斯黑德_(北卡罗莱纳州)|纳格斯黑德]]（{{lang|en| Nags Head}}）有一名男子因遭遇大浪和强烈的离岸流溺毙，是直接因亚历克斯致死的唯一一人<ref name="tcr" />。

气旋的外围[[雨带|雨带]]令[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]普降暴雨，该州中部的降雨量最高，达178毫米<ref name="rain">{{cite web | author = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2006 | title = Rainfall from Hurricane Alex | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alex2004.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304062624/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alex2004.html }}</ref>。降水引发局部洪灾，但没有报导表明该州因此蒙受损失<ref name="regent">{{cite news |author=Michelle Vischer |year=2004 |title=Rain, rain, go away- The effects of Hurricane Alex |publisher=Regents University |accessdate=2004-08-04 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.regent.edu/news/rainy_weather_20040803.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20040804171727/http://www.regent.edu/news/rainy_weather_20040803.html |archivedate=2004-08-04 }}</ref>。[[里霍伯斯滩|里霍伯斯滩]]有三人因风暴产生的离岸流受伤，几名在码头被困的儿童必须依靠外界救援才能脱身<ref name="sd3" />。[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]有至少五人在游泳时遇到大浪和离岸流，之后需要入院治疗<ref name="sd3" />。

四名英国赛艇运动员本打算用红粉佳人号（{{lang|en|Pink Lady}}）划艇从[[圣约翰斯_(纽芬兰-拉布拉多)|圣约翰斯]]划至[[法尔茅斯_(康沃尔郡)|法尔茅斯]]并打破原有速度纪录，但他们的船在亚历克斯残留的影响下沉没，幸而四人都获丹麦货轮所救，伤情也只限于轻微脑震荡，其中一人患上[[失温症|失温症]]。沉船地点距目的地约有595公里，大概还需再划两周时间。如果不是遇上风暴，他们本有望将1896年创下的54天纪录缩短十天。<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306124240/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/3547532.stm | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/3547532.stm | title = Rescued rowers back on dry land | date = 2004-08-09 | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 2016-08-10 }}</ref>

== 善后和纪录 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Alex-_40º_N.jpg|right]]

奥克拉科克岛官员认为滞留游客会阻碍岛上的清理工作，所以下令将数百名游客撤离<ref name="Beard">{{cite news | date = 2004-08-06 | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Free Lance-Star | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ojQzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5wgGAAAAIBAJ&pg=6579,1635008&dq=ferry+evacuations+begin+on+ocracoke+island&hl=en | title = Tourists evacuate Ocracoke Island | last = Beard | first = Aaron | archive-date = 2021-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211003020709/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ojQzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5wgGAAAAIBAJ&pg=6579%2C1635008&dq=ferry+evacuations+begin+on+ocracoke+island&hl=en }}</ref>。这些游客搭乘校车前往哈特拉斯岛，再根据需要自行决定是否要租车。还有部分游客乘轮渡疏散到[[海德县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|海德县]]的[[斯旺阔特_(北卡罗莱纳州)|斯旺阔特]]（{{lang|en|Swan Quarter}}），再乘校车到附近的[[博福特县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|博福特县]]城市[[华盛顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|华盛顿]]（{{lang|en|Washington}}），然后选择租车或是寻找住处。亚历克斯过去三天后，奥克拉科克岛于8月6日重新向游客开放。次周星期五，由于又有另一场风暴来袭，外滩群岛再度发布撤离令，但最终这只是虚惊一场<ref name="okra" />。[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]]官员请求[[美国国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]协助清理工作。北卡罗莱纳州交通部做好在风暴离境后马上开始清理道路的准备。<ref name="ale">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | year = 2004 | title = Stronger-than-expected Hurricane Alex grazes Outer Banks | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=P7RAAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8yAGAAAAIBAJ&pg=5003,3699867&dq=stronger-than-expected+hurricane+alex+grazes+outer+banks&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211003020753/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=P7RAAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8yAGAAAAIBAJ&pg=5003%2C3699867&dq=stronger-than-expected+hurricane+alex+grazes+outer+banks&hl=en }}</ref>

飓风亚历克斯标志着2004年大西洋飓风季成为1954年后开局第五晚的大西洋飓风季<ref name="late">{{cite news | author = CNN.com | year = 2004 | title = Hurricane Alex heads out to sea | accessdate = 2008-12-18 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.cnn.com/2004/WEATHER/08/03/alex/index.html | archivedate = 2008-12-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081218050952/http://www.cnn.com/2004/WEATHER/08/03/alex/index.html }}</ref>。[[1977年大西洋飓风季|1977年]]的[[飓风安妮塔|飓风安妮塔]]直到8月29日才形成，是1954年后大西洋飓风季最晚的开局<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archivedate = 2016-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810161332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt }}</ref>。同时，亚历克斯还是[[1973年大西洋飓风季|1973年]]的飓风爱伦过后唯一在北纬38°以北达到三级飓风强度的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]，并且亚历克斯的强度还要超过爱伦<ref name="disc19" />。此外，1950年起只有五个热带气旋在进入加拿大水域后还达到大型飓风标准，亚历克斯便是其中之一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=en&n=98B94FB2-1 | title = Canadian Marine Forecast Area Statistics Tables | publisher = Environment and Climate Change Canada | accessdate = 2016-08-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160807062501/http://www2.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=en&n=98B94FB2-1 | archivedate = 2016-08-07 }}</ref>。

